name: Data quality indicators - no obtrusive measures
description: The data is from a workshop given by Erin Buchanan and Flavio Azevedo at SIPS 2019. You can check out that workshop and project here: https://osf.io/X53KN/. Participants were given meaning in life surveys with questions on resiliency, meaning, and a few demographic questions.
citation: Buchanan, E.M. (2019). Data quality indicators - no obtrusive measures. doi: 10.17605/OSF.IO/3Y2EX
keywords: data, quality, open data, shareable, meaning, resiliency

affiliation: Harrisburg University of Science and Technology
